  "recipeInstructions": [
    "To prepare the spice mix, grind all of the spices, except the ground cumin, cinnamon and coriander, in a spice grinder or with a mortar and pestle. Then mix them with the ready-ground spices and sprinkle into a heavy-based frying pan. Cook over a medium heat, stirring constantly, until they turn dark brown; don't let them burn. Tip onto a plate and leave to cool, then store in a sealed jar until needed."
  ],
